	<section id="homepage_news_list" class="homepage-news-list" aria-label="Newslist"><article id="hp_news_article_1" class="cf" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article"><header class="cf"><h1 class="title" itemprop="name headline" id="hp_news_article_1_title">
		<a href="/apps/news/article/1182792">
								DEA will be closed for Students on Friday, March 13
							</a>
						</h1>
					</header><section class="summary cf" itemprop="description" aria-labelledby="hp_news_article_1_title"><a href="/apps/news/article/1182792" class="thumbnail cf">
									<img src="https://3.files.edl.io/a9ac/20/03/13/022817-c5331f11-2ac3-4595-8c28-1296fbdb702b.png" alt="Google Classroom"></a>
							<p>
								In order to ensure that we can adequately prepare for the unknown factors surrounding COVID-19, the David Ellis Academies will be closed on Friday, March 13 for students.<br><br>If it becomes necessary to close the school buildings for an extended period of time, Google Classroom will be an instrumental part of the online learning environment.  Therefore, staff members will be reporting to receive additional Google Classroom training.<br><br>We understand that this may be an inconvenience to some, so we apologize for the late notice.  We were planning to be closed on Monday, however, due to the closing of many of the surrounding districts, we have decided to close for students tomorrow.<br><br>Thank you for your understanding.
							</p>
						</section></article><article id="hp_news_article_2" class="cf" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article"><header class="cf"><h1 class="title" itemprop="name headline" id="hp_news_article_2_title">
