								No School - Snow Day
							</a>
						</h1>
					</header><section class="summary cf" itemprop="description" aria-labelledby="hp_news_article_4_title"><p>
								Due to inclement weather David Ellis Academy will be closed Tuesday, November 12th.
							</p>
						</section></article><article id="hp_news_article_5" class="cf" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article"><header class="cf"><h1 class="title" itemprop="name headline" id="hp_news_article_5_title">
		<a href="/apps/news/article/1079986">
								No School on Friday and Monday!
							</a>
						</h1>
					</header><section class="summary cf" itemprop="description" aria-labelledby="hp_news_article_5_title"><a href="/apps/news/article/1079986" class="thumbnail cf">
									<img src="https://3.files.edl.io/e1ec/19/08/29/201637-c3dd4f44-4753-41cd-be32-6bdd32c9bb23.jpg" alt=""></a>
							<p>
								Wow!  What an awesome first week we had a DEA. We are truly off to a great start.  It was wonderful meeting many of you this week and  I hope to see more of you on Tuesday.<br><br>As a reminder, there will be no school on Friday, August 30 and Monday, September 2 to honor the contributions workers have made to the strength, prosperity, and well-being of our country.  As a worker, we hope you have a RESTFUL Labor Day Weekend!
							</p>
						</section></article><article id="hp_news_article_6" class="cf" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Article"><header class="cf"><h1 class="title" itemprop="name headline" id="hp_news_article_6_title">
