							<p>
								Tomorrow is the first day of school for the 2019-2020 School Year!  All students may wear their DEA t-shirts and jeans.  School begins at 7:55am.  Breakfast and lunch will be provided.  We look forward to seeing your bright faces in the morning!
							</p>
